->fs install
@node install Installation
The installation is done with the AmigaInternational Installer. It is not
part of this package but can be found for example on Aminet.

To use CDCat you need at least:

    - OS 2.0, 2 MB RAM and a 020 processor
    - @{" MUI " link mui} 3.3 or higher
    - XPK, if you want your catalogs to be packed automatically

To get most out of CDCat you should use it on an Amiga with some harddisk
space and enough RAM (8 MB)

CDCat supports @{" PowerPC " link ppcnotes} boards with phase5's PPC system.

NOTE: CDCat will crash on an MC68000 processor. But you wouldn't have
      enough speed for good working anyway.
@endnode
